@startuml
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "AWS AppSync" as AppSync
participant "AWS Cognito" as Cognito
participant "Lambda Functions" as Lambda
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "Elasticsearch" as ES
participant "S3 Data Lake" as S3

Frontend -> Cognito: User authentication
Cognito --> Frontend: Authentication token

Frontend -> AppSync: GraphQL API request
AppSync -> Lambda: Invoke Lambda function
Lambda -> DynamoDB: Query/Update data
DynamoDB --> Lambda: Return data
Lambda --> AppSync: Return processed data
AppSync --> Frontend: GraphQL API response

Frontend -> Lambda: Trigger data aggregation
Lambda -> "External Sources": Fetch data
"External Sources" --> Lambda: Return raw data
Lambda -> DynamoDB: Store processed data
DynamoDB -> Lambda: Trigger DynamoDB Stream
Lambda -> ES: Update Elasticsearch index

Frontend -> Lambda: Search request
Lambda -> ES: Query Elasticsearch
ES --> Lambda: Return search results
Lambda --> Frontend: Display search results

Lambda -> S3: Archive data for long-term storage

Frontend -> Lambda: Update user preferences
Lambda -> DynamoDB: Store user preferences
DynamoDB -> Lambda: Trigger DynamoDB Stream
Lambda -> ES: Update user profile in Elasticsearch

Frontend -> Lambda: Request personalized recommendations
Lambda -> ES: Query based on user preferences
ES --> Lambda: Return personalized content
Lambda --> Frontend: Display recommendations
@enduml